WEBVTT

00:00.545 --> 00:01.524
There are two kinds of folks

00:01.551 --> 00:03.151
who sit around thinking
about how to kill people:

00:03.485 --> 00:05.211
Psychopaths and mystery writers.

00:05.449 --> 00:06.471
I'm the kind that pays better.

00:06.872 --> 00:07.471
Who am I?

00:07.561 --> 00:08.700
I'm Rick Castle.

00:08.701 --> 00:09.101
Castle.

00:09.135 --> 00:09.795
Castle.

00:09.796 --> 00:11.796
I really am ruggedly
handsome, aren't I?

00:11.942 --> 00:14.132
Every writer needs inspiration.
And I found mine.

00:14.342 --> 00:15.161
Detective Kate Beckett.

00:15.196 --> 00:16.216
- Beckett.
- Beckett.

00:16.251 --> 00:18.157
- Nikki Heat?
- The character he's basing on you.

00:18.203 --> 00:19.689
And thanks to my
friendship with the mayor,

00:19.690 --> 00:20.690
I get to be on her case.

00:20.724 --> 00:22.667
I would be happy to
let you spank me.

00:22.702 --> 00:23.578
And together, we catch killers

00:24.526 --> 00:25.514
we make a pretty good team,
you know?

00:25.515 --> 00:26.515
Like Starsky and Hutch.

00:26.649 --> 00:27.343
Turner and Hooch.

00:27.706 --> 00:28.773
You do remind me a little of Hooch.

00:29.346 --> 00:31.749
♪ I get up in the morning ♪

00:31.750 --> 00:33.815
♪ 'bout a quarter to 5:00 ♪

00:33.816 --> 00:36.952
♪ work this damn job just
to stay alive, yeah ♪

00:36.953 --> 00:40.118
♪ oh, I go to bed about
a quarter to 10:00 ♪

00:40.119 --> 00:44.721
♪ got to go and do
it all over again ♪

